<p rend="chapter">Akkharuttarikayamakagāthā</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="105"><hi rend="paranum">105</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Nonānino nanūnāni nanenāni nanānino,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Nunnānenāni nūna na nānanaṃ nānanena no.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="106"><hi rend="paranum">106</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Sāre surāsure sārī rasasārasarissaro,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Rasasārarase sāri surāsurasarassire.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="107"><hi rend="paranum">107</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Devānaṃ nandano devo devadeva na nandi no,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Vedadīnena vedana vedi vedana vedino.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="108"><hi rend="paranum">108</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Devāsane nisinno so devadevo sasāsane,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Nisinnānaṃ sadevānaṃ desesi dassanāsanaṃ.</p>
